{"tid":1728144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推俾民記、文陣、全文義政會睇到","createTime":"2019-11-16T17:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T17:55:30.000Z","uid":283704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c1df7ba5cb6115f32623159fdb6b5b14efed1a56","tid":1728144,"uid":283704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:49:41.000Z","msg":"相信手足其實心底裏面都有個嘅念<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n大家都<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">好想贏</span></span>、大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一定要贏</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n五個月以嚟抗爭嘅方式不斷係和例非&mdash;＞deadline&mdash;＞勇武&mdash;＞事後討論（民調），而我想講嘅係，關於我哋希望爭取嘅目標。我哋由五大訴求增加到解散（重組）警隊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋要嘅係民主與自由，手足嘅行到成日都俾人話會失民意，好！咁大家就再做民調，內容係關於香港人嘅意願。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日話失民意、要留守又要撤退，冇大台真係好難做決定啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！最後，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝黑警長命百歲，百病纏身。"},{"pid":"e197114da46e8ca32bb489853e9c45db701a64f3","tid":1728144,"uid":283704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:52:00.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<br />\n起底可能見到我有空白期，如果我係mon po狗我永世享大灣區。"},{"pid":"bf48ed9410ab9f8bab9bfd4346a86e8086290dbf","tid":1728144,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:55:30.000Z","msg":"政府打緊公關戰同輿論戰，口誅筆伐黎解散呢場運動，手足知唔知我地下一步要點做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1728096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1728096</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}